{"article_id":"wvcFxrP8qtAV1YUT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Arizona Republican Sen. Jeff Flake was interviewed today on NBC 's Meet the Press .","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"He told host Chuck Todd","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that as an anti-Trump republican , he could not be re-elected in 2018 .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"While this may be true to a certain extent ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"his 2018 re-election problems began","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"well before President Trump even held the 2016 GOP nomination .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"\" I love the senate .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"I love this institution .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"I love the Congress .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"I ' m not leaving","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"because of any ill will towards my colleagues or this place .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"This is a great system of government , \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Sen. Flake told the host .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" So , why ya leavin ' ? \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Todd interjected.","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"\" \" I just can ' t -","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"as a Republican","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"who believes in free trade , limited government , economic freedom ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"I couldn ' t be re-elected in my party right now .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Somebody","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"who voices reservations","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"about where the president is","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"or criticizes his behavior like last night ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"it ' s tough to be re-elected in a Republican primary . \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Sen. Flake went on to say","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that the Republican party is now the party of Trump .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"If Sen. Flake ' s statement was correct ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"it would make since then that as an anti-Trump senator , he would have a hard time","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"getting re-elected .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"But , Sen. Flake neglects to admit","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"his intra-party squabbles started","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"almost as soon as he entered office in 2012 .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"In a 2015 Washington Post article , former ardent Flake supporters","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"who thought","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"they were sending a bona-fide conservative to Washington","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"condemned Flake","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"that he was an embarrassment to the ideology . \"","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"In the 2012 race for the seat","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"he now holds ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"he won the endorsement of the Senate Conservatives Fund , a group","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"established by then-Sen. Jim DeMint","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"( R-S.C. )","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"to elect more rock-ribbed candidates . ``","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Now the same group is threatening to support a primary challenger","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"three years before Flake is up for reelection .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Ken Cuccinelli II , the fund ' s president , said in a statement","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that Flake has been \" an embarrassment \" to conservatives .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"\" Whether it ' s supporting amnesty , gun control , Obamacare funding , or the president ' s failed foreign policy ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Senator Flake has betrayed the voters","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"who sent him to Washington","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"and should be replaced with a true conservative in 2018 , \"","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Cuccinelli said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"\" At the time , Sen. Flake defended his rogue positions as personal integrity","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"and dismissed any concerns","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"he would not be able to be re-elected .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"\" Life ' s too short , \"","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"he said this week .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"\" Certainly my political life is too short","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"to worry about these kinds of things .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"I would not serve my constituents well","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"by being in lockstep with the party .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"I wouldn ' t be able to justify the time","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"it takes away from my family and everything else","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"if I were just go-along-to-get-along . \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"But other critics ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"including his own constituents ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"argued","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"the man","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"they sent to Washington","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"had all but disappeared .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"\" There is something","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that ' s fundamentally changed","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"since he ' s been in the Senate , \"","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"said Dwight Kadar , a retired businessman and Republican activist","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"who came to the Rotary luncheon with a \" Don ' t Tread on Me \" pin on his jacket .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"\" In fact , I told him ...","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"' I don ' t recognize you anymore .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"I don ' t think","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"you ' re really representing Northern Arizona and its values. ' ? \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"More specifically , many Arizonan 's were upset with Sen. Flake 's role in the Gang of 8 illegal immigration bill","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"which would have given amnesty to thousands of illegal aliens .","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"In 2013 , `` the White Mountains Conservatives organization ( asked ) voters to recall two state senators","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"for helping to overwhelmingly pass","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"( 68-32 )","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"the recent 1,200-page immigration reform bill through the Senate .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"\" In a representative republic , we expect those","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"who run as conservatives","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"to stay faithful to their calling , \"","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"the group 's president Karen MacKean said .","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"MacKean even said","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"she asked Flake to host a town-hall style meeting with constituents .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"At the time ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"she said","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"\" So far I have gotten no response .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"If they continue to ignore us ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"they will see more and more of us","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"standing up for the Constitution . \"","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Today ,","depth":4},{"id":99,"text":"polling at 18 % favorably in his home state ,","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"it is obvious that Sen. Flake could not be re-elected .","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"But how much of that is due to personal opposition to President Trump remains unclear .","depth":3},{"id":102,"text":"It would be much more apt to say that Trump was elected in 2916","depth":3},{"id":103,"text":"because of constituents angry at politicians such as Sen. Flake","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"who betrayed their base","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"rather than to say","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"that Sen. Flake can not be re-elected","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"because of his opposition to President Trump .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":215,"left":205,"right":214,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":187,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":113,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":110,"right":112,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pare